public class LinuxLocalServiceImpl
extends com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.impl.CapabilityImpl
implements LinuxLocalService

An implementation of the model object 'Linux Local Service'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Executable Path
  • Service Account
  • Service Description
  • Service Name
  • Service Status
  • Startup Run Level Five
  • Startup Run Level Four
  • Startup Run Level One
  • Startup Run Level Six
  • Startup Run Level Three
  • Startup Run Level Two
  • Startup Run Level Zero
  • Startup Type
